            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a parent, I am truly happy with my decision to enroll my child at TGS Adarsh Vidyalaya. The school provides a perfect balance between quality education and affordability. What stands out most is the strong academic focus — the teachers ensure that every child understands the concepts thoroughly and builds a solid foundation.\n\nEven though the school is not overly luxurious, it has everything a student needs to learn and grow — well-structured classrooms, a disciplined environment, dedicated teachers, and supportive staff. I especially appreciate the personal attention given to students. The teachers are approachable and regularly update us about our child’s progress.\n\nThe residential facility is also well-managed. The hostel feels safe, clean, and homely, with nutritious food and proper supervision. It’s reassuring to see how much care is taken for each child’s wellbeing.\n\nTGS Adarsh Vidyalaya truly lives up to its vision of providing quality education at an affordable cost. It’s comforting to know that my child is in good hands, receiving an education that emphasizes both academic excellence and character building.\n\nI would highly recommend TGS Adarsh Vidyalaya to any parent looking for a school that combines discipline, values, and strong academics in a caring environment",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
